00:13:50.880 --> 00:13:52.870
<font color="#ffffff">Ab 50, 55 - das muss man diskutieren.</font>

241
00:13:53.020 --> 00:13:54.510
<font color="#ffffff">Aber in der Schweiz</font>

242
